title: Readout of the President’s Meeting with CEOs | The White House
content: This afternoon, the President met with CEOs from a variety of sectors, who shared how their businesses are thriving and contributing to our economic growth. The CEOs described how Bidenomics is leading to a resilient labor market along with an investment boom in construction, manufacturing, and clean energy, creating new opportunities for businesses and workers. The President and business leaders underscored the importance of public sector-enabled, private sector-led investments as the Biden-Harris Administration kicks off its third Investing in America tour.Attendees:###
